h1 My problem

form name="problemForm" ng-submit="submit(problemForm)"
  p What is your problem about? Choose what is putting you or your family at immediate risk.

  fieldset.m-zebra
    dl ng-repeat="c in categoriesData"
      dd ng-repeat="(name, label) in c"
        label.m-block: input>(
          type="radio"
          value="{{name}}"
          name="category"
          ng-model="category.selected"
          ng-required="true"
        )  {{label}}

  p Please note: if you have more than one legal problem, you can complete the tool more than once.
